1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:31,836
=Episode 12=
(Heavens above,)

3
00:00:31,837 --> 00:00:34,624
(let me tell you a secret.)

4
00:00:34,625 --> 00:00:36,995
(I fell in love with him long ago.)

5
00:00:47,620 --> 00:00:49,260
Ye...

6
00:01:24,620 --> 00:01:25,739
This freaking weather

7
00:01:25,740 --> 00:01:27,060
is so unbearably hot.

8
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:29,300
I'm sweating so much!

9
00:01:29,620 --> 00:01:31,939
(This demon
can actually forcibly summon me?)

10
00:01:31,940 --> 00:01:33,620
(Who exactly is she?)

11
00:01:34,820 --> 00:01:36,139
My name is He Xi,

12
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:37,580
the physician of Baihua Hall.

13
00:02:00,820 --> 00:02:01,819
Why is my mind

14
00:02:01,820 --> 00:02:03,340
full of him?

15
00:02:06,820 --> 00:02:07,900
He Xi.

16
00:02:09,580 --> 00:02:12,099
You've had plenty of suitors.

17
00:02:12,100 --> 00:02:14,060
You can't be acting lovestruck.

18
00:02:15,100 --> 00:02:16,819
But he's different.

19
00:02:16,820 --> 00:02:18,620
The moment I see him,

20
00:02:19,020 --> 00:02:21,060
I feel this strange sense
of familiarity.

21
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:25,900
You've only met him once.

22
00:02:26,380 --> 00:02:27,900
What's so special about him?

23
00:02:28,380 --> 00:02:29,659
White hair,

24
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:30,980
unknown origin,

25
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:33,780
small eyes, long nose.

26
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:43,620
(He appeared when I blew the whistle
the last two times.)

27
00:02:44,540 --> 00:02:46,340
(What if...)

28
00:02:54,580 --> 00:02:55,500
I...

29
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,100
I'm drunk. It's time to sleep.

30
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,339
This isn't an illusion.

31
00:03:22,340 --> 00:03:24,500
Miss, could you come out?

32
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:26,780
I have some questions

33
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:29,340
and hope you can enlighten me.

34
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:33,299
May I ask,

35
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:34,579
what brings you here

36
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:36,180
so late at night?

37
00:03:36,460 --> 00:03:39,060
Where did that jade whistle come from?

38
00:03:39,140 --> 00:03:41,019
It was a gift from my master.

39
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:43,100
Where is your master now?

40
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:46,660
He set off on his travels
when I was young

41
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:48,179
and never returned.

42
00:03:48,180 --> 00:03:51,100
My memories from before becoming a god
are completely gone.

43
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:53,620
This whistle can summon me,

44
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:55,900
so I believe it must be tied to my past.

45
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:57,699
If your master returns,

46
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:59,940
please inform me.

47
00:04:01,180 --> 00:04:02,340
I'll take my leave then.

48
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:05,620
I...

49
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:17,460
Did your master return?

50
00:04:20,020 --> 00:04:21,060
No, I blew it by accident.

51
00:04:21,140 --> 00:04:22,300
Accident.

52
00:04:35,060 --> 00:04:35,899
Um...

53
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:37,780
My third wish

54
00:04:37,940 --> 00:04:39,939
is for you

55
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:41,339
to work for me.

56
00:04:41,340 --> 00:04:42,339
Work for you?

57
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,939
I'm just a weak woman

58
00:04:43,940 --> 00:04:45,939
practicing medicine in troubled times,

59
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:47,899
raising two children I picked up.

60
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:49,499
It's inevitable I'll be bullied.

61
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:51,339
There's also heavy work in the hall

62
00:04:51,340 --> 00:04:54,100
I can't handle alone.

63
00:05:01,860 --> 00:05:03,300
You're a demon,

64
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:07,300
and you can't even lift

65
00:05:08,540 --> 00:05:10,620
or carry things?

66
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:17,820
I was sent by heaven

67
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:21,620
to kill you.

68
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:28,380
I...

69
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:29,940
I'm just...

70
00:05:32,860 --> 00:05:33,940
(Idiot.)

71
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:36,420
(It's too late to realize the danger.)

72
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:38,420
(If I can't live,)

73
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:41,500
(then die with me.)

74
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:53,940
You don't need to be afraid

75
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:55,860
or explain yourself.

76
00:05:56,500 --> 00:05:58,740
I can see your demon heart clearly,

77
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:01,300
and I know your power is weak,

78
00:06:01,980 --> 00:06:03,420
no different from a mortal.

79
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:09,619
The people here respect you deeply.

80
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:10,740
You must be

81
00:06:11,180 --> 00:06:13,180
a good demon.

82
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:16,540
Staying here as a worker
isn't a problem.

83
00:06:17,940 --> 00:06:19,620
I can keep watch over you

84
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:21,940
and wait for your master's return.

85
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:24,979
If I'm a demon,

86
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:27,060
then having you watch me is even better.

87
00:06:27,740 --> 00:06:28,619
From now on,

88
00:06:28,620 --> 00:06:29,980
you're my worker,

89
00:06:31,420 --> 00:06:32,940
and I'm your boss.

90
00:06:33,220 --> 00:06:34,500
Together,

91
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:36,419
we'll contribute

92
00:06:36,420 --> 00:06:37,740
to this village's medical care.

93
00:06:38,220 --> 00:06:41,260
I'll follow your orders, boss.

94
00:06:47,780 --> 00:06:49,059
I'll sleep on the tree.

95
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:50,299
If you need anything,

96
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:51,500
just blow the whistle.

97
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:56,060
Zhao.

98
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:58,620
(Boss, what do you need?)

99
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:03,620
I just wanted to see if you were here.

100
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:05,420
(I'll always be here)

101
00:07:05,940 --> 00:07:07,060
(from now on.)

102
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:11,420
"I'll always be here from now on"?

103
00:07:15,980 --> 00:07:16,979
Sweep here

104
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:18,619
and over there too.

105
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:19,500
Got it.

106
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:21,500
I'm your senior, you know.

107
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:25,419
All these dirty, tiring work.

108
00:07:25,420 --> 00:07:26,539
Since you're new,

109
00:07:26,540 --> 00:07:27,940
get used to it.

110
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:30,099
He's a god.

111
00:07:30,100 --> 00:07:31,980
How dare you talk like that?

112
00:07:33,540 --> 00:07:34,740
Even gods

113
00:07:36,780 --> 00:07:38,060
can be juniors.

114
00:07:38,220 --> 00:07:39,740
Yes, Senior.

115
00:07:47,740 --> 00:07:49,420
Handle your own tasks.

116
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:52,739
He said he's the new worker
you just hired,

117
00:07:52,740 --> 00:07:54,940
so I gave him some chores.

118
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:57,299
You don't know how to manage people.

119
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:59,380
Without me, this place would fall apart.

120
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:03,860
My lady, save me!

121
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:05,939
Zhao, help me.

122
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:06,859
Hua, Bai,

123
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:08,219
prepare the hemostatics.

124
00:08:08,220 --> 00:08:09,060
Sure.

125
00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:21,099
Bai, anesthetic! Quick!

126
00:08:21,100 --> 00:08:22,100
My lady.

127
00:08:35,940 --> 00:08:38,179
We didn't sleep all night,

128
00:08:38,180 --> 00:08:39,739
and now such a big case.

129
00:08:39,740 --> 00:08:41,380
I'm exhausted.

130
00:08:51,420 --> 00:08:52,380
Come here.

131
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:06,620
My lady.

132
00:09:07,220 --> 00:09:08,499
My lady.

133
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:09,099
Go away.

134
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:10,300
My lady.

135
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:12,499
Let's go.

136
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:13,699
My lady.

137
00:09:13,700 --> 00:09:14,739
Don't look back.

138
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:15,739
Keep moving.

139
00:09:15,740 --> 00:09:17,460
In times like these,

140
00:09:18,620 --> 00:09:20,340
with war and chaos everywhere,

141
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:24,140
injured people often come here.

142
00:09:25,220 --> 00:09:27,399
I try to save whoever I can.

143
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,180
Sometimes I think to myself,

144
00:09:31,980 --> 00:09:34,220
if someone I saved

145
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:36,940
could end this chaos,

146
00:09:38,460 --> 00:09:40,900
it would all be worth it.

147
00:10:14,260 --> 00:10:15,940
What time is it now?

148
00:10:19,340 --> 00:10:20,460
Around 10.

149
00:10:21,980 --> 00:10:24,300
You've been sitting here
without moving for so long.

150
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:29,420
Why didn't you wake me?

151
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:32,300
I meditate often anyway.

152
00:10:32,980 --> 00:10:34,540
I just considered it practice.

153
00:10:34,740 --> 00:10:36,660
Did I snore?

154
00:10:37,620 --> 00:10:39,259
Snore?

155
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:41,020
You sounded like thunder.

156
00:10:45,820 --> 00:10:48,300
I don't usually snore.

157
00:10:48,340 --> 00:10:50,220
I must've been too tired today.

158
00:10:56,900 --> 00:10:57,859
Lady He,

159
00:10:57,860 --> 00:10:59,900
the village chief is summoning you.

160
00:11:00,340 --> 00:11:01,580
Zhao, let's go.

161
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:04,540
We're almost there.

162
00:11:05,980 --> 00:11:07,099
- Boss.
- Lady He.

163
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,220
Are you alright?

164
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:09,540
Can you still walk?

165
00:11:10,380 --> 00:11:12,580
I'm fine. Let's keep going.

166
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:15,020
Careful.

167
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:20,180
If you don't mind,

168
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:21,700
I can carry you.

169
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,619
Looks like I have no choice.

170
00:11:23,620 --> 00:11:24,139
Take this.

171
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:25,140
Alright.

172
00:11:25,740 --> 00:11:26,820
Get on.

173
00:11:27,900 --> 00:11:29,420
Let's go.

174
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:32,460
Slowly now.

175
00:11:34,780 --> 00:11:36,460
Lady He, be careful.

176
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:48,699
Chief Zhang, let me check your pulse.

177
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:50,060
Xi, you're here.

178
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:51,459
Sorry to trouble you.

179
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:53,180
Thank you for coming all this way.

180
00:11:53,220 --> 00:11:55,099
Not at all.

181
00:11:55,100 --> 00:11:56,219
You've helped us

182
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:58,020
plenty too at Baihua Hall.

183
00:11:58,500 --> 00:11:59,900
Open your mouth.

184
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:11,019
Your condition is quite serious.

185
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:12,259
I'll use acupuncture

186
00:12:12,260 --> 00:12:13,540
to ease the symptoms.

187
00:12:14,380 --> 00:12:15,219
Xi,

188
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:16,820
seeing you

189
00:12:17,260 --> 00:12:19,180
already makes me feel better.

190
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:23,780
You flatter me.

191
00:12:24,140 --> 00:12:27,180
I'll remove your clothes
to begin the treatment.

192
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:28,139
Okay.

193
00:12:28,140 --> 00:12:29,220
Wait!

194
00:12:32,860 --> 00:12:33,940
Boss,

195
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:35,180
allow me

196
00:12:35,380 --> 00:12:37,140
to take care of this.

197
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:38,540
Alright.

198
00:12:39,260 --> 00:12:40,660
No, wait.

199
00:12:41,860 --> 00:12:44,060
(My leg is injured.)

200
00:12:50,700 --> 00:12:51,660
No.

201
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:54,460
Don't.

202
00:12:54,740 --> 00:12:55,820
Stop.

203
00:13:03,380 --> 00:13:05,700
Why did you strip him completely?

204
00:13:06,020 --> 00:13:08,140
His fever's pretty bad.

205
00:13:08,740 --> 00:13:11,460
He'll need additional needling,

206
00:13:11,620 --> 00:13:12,579
so I

207
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:14,060
stripped him off completely.

208
00:13:16,580 --> 00:13:18,979
Chief Zhang, this is Zhao,

209
00:13:18,980 --> 00:13:20,340
my new worker.

210
00:13:20,380 --> 00:13:22,499
He's a bit rough.

211
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:24,020
Please forgive him.

212
00:13:26,580 --> 00:13:29,300
Zhao, you look very distinguished.

213
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:30,820
Pleasure to meet you.

214
00:13:32,140 --> 00:13:35,060
Chief Zhang, I've heard a lot about you.

215
00:13:35,700 --> 00:13:38,099
The pleasure is mine.

216
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:41,019
You need proper rest these days.

217
00:13:41,020 --> 00:13:43,420
I'll have Bai deliver your medicine.

218
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:45,420
Please take it regularly as prescribed.

219
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:47,699
Xi, thank you so much.

220
00:13:47,700 --> 00:13:48,580
Xi!

221
00:13:50,700 --> 00:13:52,686
Chief Zhang seems much better.
He should be fine now.

222
00:13:52,687 --> 00:13:54,440
There are more patients waiting.
Let's go back.

223
00:13:55,220 --> 00:13:55,979
Chief Zhang!

224
00:13:55,980 --> 00:13:57,580
He's not quite right in the head.

225
00:14:00,820 --> 00:14:01,940
Wait.

226
00:14:08,380 --> 00:14:09,259
Stop.

227
00:14:09,260 --> 00:14:10,700
I need to pray here.

228
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:16,020
Even if the gods hear you,

229
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:18,300
they may not respond.

230
00:14:19,140 --> 00:14:21,379
I'm praying to my own heart.

231
00:14:21,380 --> 00:14:23,780
I won't rely on some stone
to grant my wishes.

232
00:14:24,220 --> 00:14:25,340
Zhao,

233
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:26,979
can you help me?

234
00:14:26,980 --> 00:14:30,180
I need two hands to pray,

235
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:32,580
but my right hand still hurts
and I can't lift it.

236
00:14:32,620 --> 00:14:35,060
How should I help?

237
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:43,140
Close your eyes and ask your heart.

238
00:14:44,820 --> 00:14:46,180
(My name is He Xi,)

239
00:14:46,620 --> 00:14:48,660
(and I live at Baihua Hall.)

240
00:14:49,460 --> 00:14:51,180
(Heavens above,)

241
00:14:51,340 --> 00:14:53,660
(please don't bless the wrong thing.)

242
00:14:53,860 --> 00:14:56,099
(What I said earlier was just talk.)

243
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:57,780
(Don't take it seriously.)

244
00:14:58,020 --> 00:15:00,540
(Please bless the one I love)

245
00:15:01,100 --> 00:15:03,060
(so that he may love me too.)

246
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:11,220
That bell sounds nice.

247
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:19,899
(How bold of you, Ye Zhao.)

248
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:22,940
(Have you fallen for this demon?)

249
00:15:26,250 --> 00:15:27,959
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

250
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:30,809
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

251
00:15:30,810 --> 00:15:33,549
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

252
00:15:33,550 --> 00:15:35,179
♪Let the long shadows♪

253
00:15:35,180 --> 00:15:40,780
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

254
00:15:40,830 --> 00:15:42,429
♪If in a dream♪

255
00:15:42,430 --> 00:15:45,189
♪I can hear your voice♪

256
00:15:45,190 --> 00:15:48,039
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

257
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:50,639
♪Let it be us♪

258
00:15:50,640 --> 00:15:55,429
♪drawing endlessly close♪

259
00:15:55,430 --> 00:15:57,189
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

260
00:15:57,190 --> 00:15:59,840
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

261
00:16:00,060 --> 00:16:02,779
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

262
00:16:02,780 --> 00:16:04,429
♪Not even in time♪

263
00:16:04,430 --> 00:16:10,089
♪to tell you how I feel♪

264
00:16:10,090 --> 00:16:11,629
♪If the rain won't stop♪

265
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:14,379
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

266
00:16:14,380 --> 00:16:17,349
♪Let love go on♪

267
00:16:17,350 --> 00:16:19,899
♪Until forever♪

268
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:24,539
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

269
00:16:24,540 --> 00:16:27,149
♪Until forever♪

270
00:16:27,150 --> 00:16:34,260
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
